==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dissolving
<hw>Dis*solv"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Melting; breaking up;
vanishing.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Dis*solv"ing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Dissolving view</b></col>, <cd>a picture which grows dim
and is gradually replaced by another on the same field; -- an effect
produced by magic lanterns.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dissonance</ent>⟦br⟧
